		<title>Why is Bitcoin Referred to as a Pseudonymous Network?</title>
		<link>https://securenest.org/learn/bitcoin-as-pseudonymous-network</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Morgan Davis]]></dc:creator>
